data.description: Ready to move to Sallisaw?? This home is located in the heart of town. This three bedroom, one bath home with 1,352 sf (per CH) is constructed on a corner lot with 7,600 sf (according to plat). This home has a new privacy fence, updated kitchen and bathroom. What was once the garage has been converted to a bonus room, and is heated and cooled with a window unit, the rest of the home is central heat and air. This property is located within a close to the elementary school, shopping, and restaurants.
